# Privacy Policy — Hour by Hour

_Last updated: May 23, 2026_

Hour by Hour ("the app," "we," "us") is built privacy-first.

**Your data stays on your device.** Everything you enter — goals, commitments,
logged activities, schedule, and settings — is stored locally on your device
only. We have no server, we do not collect this data, and it is never transmitted
to us or anyone else. We cannot see it. Deleting the app deletes this data.

**No account, no tracking.** The app requires no account or sign-in. We use no
analytics, no advertising, and no third-party tracking. We do not sell or share
any personal information.

**Purchases.** The app offers a one-time in-app purchase to unlock full access
after a free trial. Purchases are processed by Apple. To verify your purchase
status we use RevenueCat, which may receive a randomly generated identifier and
your purchase transaction details solely to confirm access. This is not linked
to your name, email, or identity, and is never used for advertising or tracking.

**Children.** The app is intended for users aged 13 and older.

**Changes.** We may update this policy; the date above reflects the latest version.

**Contact.** Questions? Email **[TheZionsellers@icloud.com]**.
